title: 10 Chess Books - June 2016 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 chess book/magazines for this month collected from various sources:

01. New In Chess Magazine No. 4 (2014)
02. New In Chess Magazine No. 4 (2015)
03. New In Chess Yearbook 61
04. New In Chess Yearbook 62
05. New In Chess Yearbook 64
06. People, Places, Checkmates by Alexey Root
07. Secrets of Grandmaster Play by John Nunn
08. The Art of the Middle Game by Jeres & Kotov
09. The Week in Chess (#1121-1125) - May 2016
10. The World Chess Championship - A History
